        <detaileddescription>
<para>Performs comprehensive validation and balancing on a weapon item:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Normalizes ID prefix to &quot;Weapon_&quot;</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Clamps combat stats to valid ranges</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Validates weapon type and caliber compatibility</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Balances rarity based on combat effectiveness</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Generates default description if empty</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="inout">item</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Weapon item to validate and balance (modified in-place)</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>This function modifies the item parameter directly </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Combat stats are balanced relative to each other </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
